ACTION=="add|bind", SUBSYSTEM=="platform", DRIVER=="amd_x3d_vcache", RUN+="/usr/bin/systemd-tmpfiles --create /usr/lib/tmpfiles.d/x3d_toggle-tmpfiles.conf"

## Udev rule for the X3D Toggle Project
## `sysfs.rules` installs to `/usr/lib/udev/rules.d/99-x3d_toggle-sysfs.rules`
## Dynamically re-applies group ownership and permissions to the amd_x3d_mode 
## sysfs attributes whenever the amd_x3d_vcache driver is re-bound or probed,
## ensuring seamless backend execution without breaking DAC isolation limits.
## end of file